text: Veronika Sharametsyeva (born 1 December 1982) is a road cyclist from Belarus.Veronika Sharametsyeva cyclebase.nl She represented her nation in the road race at the 2005 UCI Road World Championships but failed to finish. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1982 births Category:Belarusian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
